    "Html": "Hi to all,<br>\r\ni'm currently building a prototype for a new application with an ApplicationMenu.<br>\r\nIn that application there is no need for a Ribbon, but we will use an RibbonApplicationMenu with a RibbonQuickAccessToolbar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSo here my XAML-Code (only the structure):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">\r\n<p>&lt;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">ribbon</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">RibbonWindow</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> x</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\">Class</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Client.Window2&quot; [...] </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\">Visibility</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Visible&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Background</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;GhostWhite&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> WindowState</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Normal&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> WindowStyle</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;SingleBorderWindow&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> MaxWidth</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;460&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> MaxHeight</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;140&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> WindowStartupLocation</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;CenterScreen&quot;&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DockPanel</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> x</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\">Name</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;ContentArea&quot;&gt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">    &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">StackPanel</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Orientation</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Horizontal&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> DockPanel.Dock</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Top&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">        &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">ribbon</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">RibbonApplicationMenu</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> DockPanel.Dock</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Top&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> HorizontalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Left&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> VerticalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Top&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n        [...]<br>\r\n        </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">ribbon</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">RibbonApplicationMenu</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n        </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">ribbon</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">RibbonQuickAccessToolBar</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> CanUserCustomize</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;False&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> VerticalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Top&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> HorizontalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Left&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n        </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">[...]</span>        <br>\r\n        <span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">ribbon</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">RibbonQuickAccessToolBar</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">    &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">StackPanel</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">    &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DockPanel</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> DockPanel.Dock</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Top&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n    </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">StackPanel</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> x</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\">Name</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;RecordArea&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Width</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;100&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Background</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;DarkBlue&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> VerticalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Stretch&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> HorizontalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Left&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> DockPanel.Dock</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Left&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Orientation</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Vertical&quot;&gt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">StackPanel</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n    </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">StackPanel</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> x</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\">Name</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;WorkflowArea&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Background</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;DarkBlue&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> DockPanel.Dock</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Right&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Width</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;100&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> HorizontalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Right&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Orientation</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Vertical&quot;&gt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">StackPanel</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n    </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">StackPanel</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> x</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\">Name</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;InfoAudioArea&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> DockPanel.Dock</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Top&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> VerticalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Stretch&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> HorizontalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Stretch&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Width</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Auto&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Height</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Auto&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Background</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;LightCoral&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Orientation</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Vertical&quot;&gt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">StackPanel</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n    </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DockPanel</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DockPanel</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">ribbon</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">RibbonWindow</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<br>\r\nHere the visual result: <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/99509916@N00/3005427290/sizes/o/\">http://www.flickr.com/photos/99509916@N00/3005427290/sizes/o/</a><br>\r\n<br>\r\nMy problem is that the style of the RibbonApplicationMenu changes the size of the other panels (see last screenshot in the picture).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDoes anyone know a way to avoid that?<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBest regards<br>\r\nCarsten<br>\r\n<br>\r\n",
